abstract: New York Jets quarterback Mark Sanchez has chance to re-energize Jets against weak defense of winless Miami Dolphins.
snippet: Monday’s game against the Dolphins, a winless team with a weak defense, presents Mark Sanchez with a chance to energize the Jets.
lead_paragraph: Monday’s game against the Dolphins, a winless team with a weak defense, presents Mark Sanchez with a chance to energize the Jets.

headline.main: Dolphins Give Sanchez a Chance to Iron Out Inconsistencies
headline.print_headline: Dolphins Give Sanchez a Chance to Iron Out Inconsistencies
headline.seo: Sanchez Can Energize Jets With Win Against Dolphins
